[
  {
    "start": 23.297,
    "end": 26.17,
    "text": "The line thins out to steady hum,"
  },
  {
    "start": 26.17,
    "end": 30.16,
    "text": "as two axises become one."
  },
  {
    "start": 30.16,
    "end": 31.596,
    "text": "Trickly tiny runnel,"
  },
  {
    "start": 31.596,
    "end": 33.031,
    "text": "warped into a tunnel."
  },
  {
    "start": 33.031,
    "end": 35.984,
    "text": "Steady as she goes,"
  },
  {
    "start": 35.984,
    "end": 39.335,
    "text": "Where it leads,"
  },
  {
    "start": 39.335,
    "end": 43.453,
    "text": "nobody knows."
  },
  {
    "start": 43.802,
    "end": 46.914,
    "text": "What is it, this funny feeling -"
  },
  {
    "start": 46.914,
    "end": 49.786,
    "text": "ominous onto it's reeling."
  },
  {
    "start": 49.786,
    "end": 52.899,
    "text": "steady over the stepping stone."
  },
  {
    "start": 52.899,
    "end": 56.09,
    "text": "Seems like someone is there,"
  },
  {
    "start": 56.09,
    "end": 59.091,
    "text": "certainly I am not alone."
  },
  {
    "start": 59.441,
    "end": 62.393,
    "text": "Peel of the dark, frame by frame,"
  },
  {
    "start": 62.393,
    "end": 65.105,
    "text": "Little guardian angel speaks my name."
  },
  {
    "start": 65.105,
    "end": 66.144,
    "text": "Troubled trembling soul at rest,"
  },
  {
    "start": 66.144,
    "end": 70.611,
    "text": "You have come home now,"
  },
  {
    "start": 70.611,
    "end": 72.206,
    "text": "You did your very best."
  },
  {
    "start": 72.206,
    "end": 75.956,
    "text": "Say - Do you, not recognize my face?"
  },
  {
    "start": 75.956,
    "end": 79.069,
    "text": "After all, do you not know this place?"
  },
  {
    "start": 79.069,
    "end": 82.26,
    "text": "Welcome, we have been up waiting"
  },
  {
    "start": 82.26,
    "end": 85.98,
    "text": "welcome home from your hibernating."
  },
  {
    "start": 86.329,
    "end": 87.605,
    "text": "confused and not terribly amused,"
  },
  {
    "start": 87.605,
    "end": 93.989,
    "text": "I think perhaps, I could get used."
  },
  {
    "start": 93.989,
    "end": 102.846,
    "text": "to a warm welcome such as this."
  },
  {
    "start": 102.846,
    "end": 107.043,
    "text": "In this place, such boundless bliss."
  },
  {
    "start": 107.394,
    "end": 110.186,
    "text": "Even the sun here seems to radiate joy,"
  },
  {
    "start": 110.186,
    "end": 113.456,
    "text": "What was it again you said Tolstoy?"
  },
  {
    "start": 113.456,
    "end": 114.653,
    "text": "Iljitjs thought his thoughts"
  },
  {
    "start": 114.653,
    "end": 116.329,
    "text": "in silent making."
  },
  {
    "start": 116.329,
    "end": 118.165,
    "text": "Slow textures render,"
  },
  {
    "start": 118.165,
    "end": 119.489,
    "text": "hardly baking."
  },
  {
    "start": 119.84,
    "end": 120.718,
    "text": "What, what?"
  },
  {
    "start": 120.718,
    "end": 122.951,
    "text": "Where.. was I just before?"
  },
  {
    "start": 122.951,
    "end": 124.628,
    "text": "Was there not a door?"
  },
  {
    "start": 124.628,
    "end": 126.063,
    "text": "What is the matter with me,"
  },
  {
    "start": 126.063,
    "end": 127.739,
    "text": "How did I come to be.."
  },
  {
    "start": 127.739,
    "end": 161.617,
    "text": "here.."
  },
  {
    "start": 161.967,
    "end": 164.76,
    "text": "Certainly I have seen this place,"
  },
  {
    "start": 164.76,
    "end": 168.431,
    "text": "I know it better then my own face."
  },
  {
    "start": 168.431,
    "end": 172.5,
    "text": "Something I have always known,"
  },
  {
    "start": 172.5,
    "end": 175.293,
    "text": "How could I forget my home."
  }
]
